snippet.title: Ghostland Yard | Official Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2051130/Ghostland_Yard/

Uncover the truth about the Ghostland Yard investigators disappearance in this challenging 2D precision platformer. In this early access, travel through 4 differents environment in more than 80 hand-crafted levels to find your friends! 

Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/rAbVepnnbA
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/studio_obelisk
